---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About AutomatorLabs | Free Financial Calculators and Guides"
  description="Learn how AutomatorLabs creates free financial calculators and educational guides focused on clarity, transparency, and understanding the numbers."
>
  <main>
    <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <ol>
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li aria-current="page">About</li>
      </ol>
    </nav>

    <header class="page-header">
      <p class="eyebrow">About AutomatorLabs</p>
      <h1>Financial tools that explain the numbers</h1>
      <p class="intro">
        AutomatorLabs provides free financial calculators and educational
        guides designed to make common money questions easier to explore and
        understand.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="content-card" aria-labelledby="mission-heading">
      <h2 id="mission-heading">Our mission</h2>
      <p>
        The mission of AutomatorLabs is to help people turn financial
        assumptions into understandable results. A calculator should do more
        than produce a number: it should make the inputs, formulas,
        limitations, and meaning of the result clear.
      </p>
      <p>
        The site covers topics such as saving, investing, retirement, debt,
        mortgages, and budgeting. Its calculators support practical scenario
        testing, while its guides explain the concepts behind those
        calculations in approachable language.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="principles" aria-labelledby="principles-heading">
      <h2 id="principles-heading">How we approach financial information</h2>
      <div class="principle-grid">
        <article>
          <h3>Clarity</h3>
          <p>
            Inputs and outputs use direct labels, and supporting explanations
            help users understand what each result represents.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h3>Transparency</h3>
          <p>
            Calculators state their assumptions and formulas so results can be
            evaluated instead of treated as unexplained answers.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h3>Understanding</h3>
          <p>
            Educational content connects the calculation to the broader
            financial idea, including common mistakes and limitations.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="explore" aria-labelledby="explore-heading">
      <div>
        <h2 id="explore-heading">Explore AutomatorLabs</h2>
        <p>
          Start with a calculator, read a related guide, or get in touch with
          feedback about the site.
        </p>
      </div>
      <nav class="page-links" aria-label="Explore AutomatorLabs">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/calculators/">Calculators</a>
        <a href="/guides/">Guides</a>
        <a href="/contact/">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    width: min(960px, calc(100% - 2rem));
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 0 5rem;
  }

  .breadcrumbs {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--muted-text-color);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .breadcrumbs ol {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.45rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .breadcrumbs li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.45rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .breadcrumbs li + li::before {
    color: var(--muted-text-color);
    content: '›';
  }

  .breadcrumbs a,
  .page-links a {
    color: var(--link-color);
  }

  .breadcrumbs a {
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .breadcrumbs a:hover,
  .page-links a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .breadcrumbs [aria-current='page'] {
    color: var(--text-color);
    font-weight: 650;
  }

  .page-header {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
    color: var(--link-color);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 4.5rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    line-height: 1.04;
  }

  .intro {
    margin: 1rem 0 0;
    color: var(--muted-text-color);
    font-size: 1.14rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .content-card,
  .explore {
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: var(--card-background);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 35px var(--shadow-color);
    padding: clamp(1.4rem, 5vw, 2.25rem);
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0 0 0.8rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .content-card p,
  .principle-grid p,
  .explore p {
    color: var(--muted-text-color);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .content-card p:last-child,
  .principle-grid p,
  .explore p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .principles {
    padding: 3.25rem 0;
  }

  .principle-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
  }

  .principle-grid article {
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: var(--card-background);
    padding: 1.25rem;
  }

  .principle-grid h3 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.08rem;
  }

  .principle-grid p {
    margin-top: 0.55rem;
  }

  .explore {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .explore p {
    max-width: 580px;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .page-links {
    display: flex;
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem 1rem;
  }

  .page-links a {
    font-weight: 750;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    main {
      padding-top: 3rem;
    }

    .principle-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .explore {
      align-items: flex-start;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }
</style>
